# UI & Component Patterns

## Visual Style

- Dark theme: backgrounds `#0A0A0A`, `#0F0F0F`, `#151515`; borders `#222`
- Accent: amber (`amber-500`, `amber-600`) for CTAs and highlights
- Currency: Philippine peso (`₱`) with `toLocaleString(undefined, { minimumFractionDigits: 2 })`
- Icons: `lucide-react`

## Component Layout

- Rounded cards: `rounded-2xl border border-[#222] p-6`
- Form labels: `text-[10px] font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider`
- Toasts: fixed top-right, auto-dismiss ~4s (see `App.tsx`)

## AI Markdown Rendering

When rendering AI output in `AIAssistant.tsx`:

- Use `react-markdown` with `rehype-sanitize`
- Block dangerous URL schemes via `urlTransform` (`javascript:`, `data:`, `vbscript:`)
- Never use `dangerouslySetInnerHTML` for AI content

## Import/Export

- Export: JSON download via data URI
- Import: enforce `MAX_IMPORT_FILE_BYTES` (1 MB) and `parseImportedTrips()` validation
- Accept only `.json` files; reset file input after import

## Domain Context

Content is Philippines-specific: expressway rules (400cc+), RFID tolls, carinderias, vulcanizing shops, RoRo ferries, Cordillera routes. Keep copy and AI prompts aligned with this context.
